Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求别人幸福的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不得不去诅咒其他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们魔法少女就是这样的构造吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  你到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对沙耶香做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松开我的手的话你的时间也会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个魔女是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经叫做美树沙耶香的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到最后了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意的话就丢掉那多余的累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就杀死那魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你做得到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你只会拖后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时撤退吧
